snippet.textDisplay:
What a fusion! The most amazing song of the 2024 so far. 

Great tune Zahoor, love your range. 

Good God REHMA, are you for real? Your voice.......gave the whole song such a melodious touch that one forget for a second what language is she singing in, though she does switch between Pashto and English, just mind blowing.......girl, keep it going, can't wait to see you become a super star! 

Of course, I see Abdullah's footprint all over this song.......you Mastro!!!... what a talent you truly are, I bow to you! 

Last but not least The Magician Mr. Xulfi, sir...... how do you even make it happen? 

#Xulfi #Abdullah Siddiqui #Zahoor #REHMA
